==English==

===Etymology===
[[Onomatopoetic]] of the sound from a [[turkey]].

===Verb===
'''gobble'''
# to put into one's mouth and swallow food hastily or greedily; to [[scoff]]
#:''He '''gobbled''' four hot dogs in three minutes.''
# To make the sound of a turkey.

